  "files": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "先生、3日前から咳が出て、昨日から熱も出ました。",
      "file": "000_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 0,
      "timestamp_end": 6
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "どのくらいの熱ですか？",
      "file": "001_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 6,
      "timestamp_end": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "今朝測ったら38.2度ありました。",
      "file": "002_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 8,
      "timestamp_end": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "喉の痛みや鼻水はありますか？",
      "file": "003_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 12,
      "timestamp_end": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "喉が痛いです。あと、体がだるくて頭も痛いです。",
      "file": "004_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 15,
      "timestamp_end": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "少し喉を見せてください。「あー」と言ってください。",
      "file": "005_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 20,
      "timestamp_end": 25
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "あーーー",
      "file": "006_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 25,
      "timestamp_end": 28
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "扁桃が腫れて赤くなっていますね。インフルエンザの検査をしましょう。",
      "file": "007_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 28,
      "timestamp_end": 35
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "...検査結果は陰性でした。普通の風邪のようです。",
      "file": "008_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 35,
      "timestamp_end": 42
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "解熱剤と咳止め、それに抗生物質を出します。扁桃腺の炎症を抑えるためです。",
      "file": "009_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 42,
      "timestamp_end": 52
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "仕事に行っても大丈夫ですか？",
      "file": "010_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 52,
      "timestamp_end": 55
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "熱が下がるまで2〜3日は自宅で休んでください。水分を十分に取ってくださいね。",
      "file": "011_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 55,
      "timestamp_end": 64
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "speaker": "doctor",
      "text": "もし39度以上の熱が続いたり、呼吸が苦しくなったら、すぐにまた来てください。",
      "file": "012_doctor.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 64,
      "timestamp_end": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "speaker": "patient",
      "text": "分かりました。ありがとうございます。",
      "file": "013_patient.mp3",
      "timestamp_start": 72,
      "timestamp_end": 76
    }
  ]
}